Update Response class in commandquery module

This commit revises the Response class in the commandquery module. It removes the existing license header and imports, significantly enhancing readability and maintenance. It also adds a series of new class attributes including client_id, request_id, reply_channel, metadata, body, cache_hit, timestamp, executed, error, and tags for future functionality.
